Plintissa waves her hand and makes her OWN star reappear.... "Liono can make
HIS star disappear but he can't take the star that i always had!..." she
thought.... "he's an idiot, my star is more powerful anyway!..." she
thought.... "i threw his star at a boulder and it wouldn't even cut it! mine
cut the boulder!.....and he can't take my star!...." she thought, taking the
star back and preventing an idiot like Liono from taking her weapons
FOREVER!.....she has all her weapons for good.... and anyway, she still had
that gun and mace she got from the base and didn't need his dumb and weak
star!....and Liono could not take her own star! (RGDan, you cannot take all
of my characters weapons! i don't except that she got her star back!....)
